: 10px;" width="80" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt;&lt;p style="font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; color: inherit; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;零&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.2; margin: 4px 0 0 0; color: inherit; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;英国改革计划结束数十年的气候行动&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign="bottom" width="28"&gt;&lt;img alt="立即收听" height="28" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihClwsFiKu8o/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; border-radius: 10px;" width="28" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;英国改革党是目前英国最受欢迎的政党。本周，在《零》节目中，阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 向改革党副领导人理查德·泰斯 (Richard Tice) 询问该党的气候和能源计划，以及为什么他称其为“净愚蠢的零”。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pNz1bjzh_xmoYtBnKiFIyKmcE9yurYnMyvZqX52TNSnwnkvyCOcbsqUrd7FKmbLPbQnzn95k0HJCT2CmikiV5GCOdzWiTablyz3Zrj_sNxQmfklpCQvDvq-5d0xNj1z1hO95FIkkFNAPRpcDnlTBIdGRXc4Sh5CUretyn_LcHB4my8X0-WvNQ_JK1Xj99X4KHJn0clA9oUjfca3WevSOniAnv_Me1axLQzWX9rah5ms9eb3GrSTG5y1q3kDaZTaN-slZQwn2U4xGxTExSCBB_M0aalPKg7RanUvrKcbiFcFmOCrSaGk6phOLOOAp8YIxZWIO4ALsAlRep-6oh_RnbUxe_vfj_C5qcdA66Ul7/Y7XSJecqU8obgCfMvFdJlIXJiBMGT1ZI/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0ZM-hvBgDr_MKXTvY0CAWu93G7_y9MRelpe-JAWrh1YGVvW91jpn77I4Y3r1MNd9HcjNFSV-BI8LgGJE8Q5U3HYij8KVzeeXQ3Ul_ILegl2RIgKTNFvdcOM_e0ErRDoIMPRl3z8sE0KKBTWFFpJ6fwZK1O1FeXUXUUy30IJMDfACrcnvq5E8IGldLzwQ5D3MHHzAf8LHG6CcdbN7u3Tou5u21UDeBk3gAmlapsEdcVu6Nsdc3nZKo8DrWbmznw6CsmI75JQZZ_FaIe1tyJebKpuYki8tk1dlW-5l27wChstS5kVSkIfekaRievVrVsHH2K18nA/HpZ5Rd1vo8F_Z2RVgq0PS8iXc9AeJdT3/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Nh7ZyI4Hb5GbQA1YuQbze_hmidrTdQFQ5aMc