: 16px;"&gt;据英国《金融时报》报道，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;中国领导人习近平&lt;/strong&gt;在与特朗普在北京举行的峰会上批评日本首相高市早苗的防务举措时，他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/WglnCYVNpKtKl5EAKxxLMuyasEZ_3WpEyCAdA9NaDic0ABTnRRhUFMNyopDvBidtaTsWlbDsUJwB2iLp14xU0ExQICkJLLzcVvgo1Jukt9ZeaqCXVB9GSOvkC4t4dw91U-rn0899D488bLG4NbuoSbV0X6uCr65cuq0qejGG8vUXhZ1KL7hBO34th7nUbqvLCcFD6kLy-XImWv9EwXE82E3wcy9cpaNIwZUQErrD9Vb2N6eVmBnw5ra80FGFvNMTbeMtYi-qEkAXuARTTQxs1XxPix8XK4lKiHiHHuJR1t-1rlsUrjxzw2I5xtcpdJE5ymr9Y6cF3U9VzyBNxpqve59odE7swucCOQOU3iOiOL3CtFZNp7o2w0EEokgEnqWdFoK4QSuyFvibKNLzr2b78gsDwOwEf1c9RcnYjlrL8JEcN5nQj3lrBiBHy1iMKqTT_9UNPggVu73DKcmNMWZaBduNAFQLYeIdryUcP7d-YElUSjPF9b43iSXaXBdeeyivNwW1_EqSO7j9RMkTeF9VdWYnShcN0ehGjbq4IA/cM3DkZXModeO-IW6MmHFDGJPVz4N7fBk/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="英国《金融时报》称习近平在特朗普峰会期间攻击日本重新军备"&gt;的言论变得十分激动&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;塞内加尔总统巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/aqzVk3elD5ADwvpp2z0w3igT9QYpY22fOHNgF0KG16Qzpmu4sk0CxtOB-fzj3SolHJC8hRivrQRaQiYn_BcdFDbB_9GnrNRrozGgaRoYrH4tu5SuLCBy25WZ56Vv5zljKnDXMPdi6V3JOeso9UBpCZZHRQGhV3MGdMwGNBh6QcdxXjQZwf4YUhkx-JohucRNnUaw0NCHUI-TpSUPYr9Xqg1Q6kXfX1L8F0A5LtFbpugS5OZY9spzRnvnr1PSlp-gmSEnlcmI1vCtRQgL73u2yTKfhYlFraWfn4UgJbJe6EJ4QmcQUSh25p9khzY3UYDSP4C1QDTfgdpNsL8cQGaxLRA3dNtinh6wC1g-y9jtUSL3oE00pGiDc7ZsWiWYJu6uSOn-V8-pMlk7siZbaF3CFA5iH1521NpioTvvGQrxiZ0G3LcDvV5E29NoGUt6KiREt9Mg5V8TopSfQ9JQQNzPF847wK9dd-E32Af7cnLK6YWzhJGmc01G2znH1xGG_1Ck_9Uk68-0rzWFbsA2oHvTBZMMkZ9wcXxt5P475nBXy-ce/sGnDQSf34-YbPTrmRmgD_kKio5w4xIJV/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="塞内加尔政府的内爆扰乱了与国际货币基金组织的债务谈判"&gt;突然解除&lt;/a&gt;总理奥斯曼·松科的职务，可能会使该国政府与国际货币基金组织陷入僵局的谈判陷入更深的混乱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;教皇利奥十四世警告世界领导人&lt;/strong&gt;不要利用&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/XyQL404zqyIgZQUSNsBf5l_8IUiDn8LGX839utwu5IXAV57HfdU90RVl7tKZouYN3G0t3xM9ugFn8a29TET7x1uNPzYne5cu4w73PLYSd2HRsJEOaj5MB-gainMfWoEi4YFvQkKahoQHwsnBvV480mdDOg1pNfnBefzCEi9kZ9GAtQ900hIug-ye-py2ukLOUCTF1nAYFqicZ_auaFm2JjmJKXOhnqwaZ99qt1JviZ4EANGJ6gpealWpqqt8w1E7A9xdXNbI_KDHWki_ZUSeydMbqs9qfp-8V2d051FrBq8zOnGszGic6BxdzvS_a-6Cnmc2q8kj2Zlhp7385z41Zz-9hX3squVpa8ROFUgfQLfwG-ubBpmZNlSc71nKHHw8FoKOcXIEYF48RrexryIxI4kTiLgpYI35JPpvB_9kKT4IbSjtqAC9jpcbS2P_UE_3tkTbQ6Nwinika3eVXGfO7bqLO6ZeDrxDFBYnYiIb8YKkiO450HTnS3Qwtn7Fu7TNPoHxsQVENrlR5nBOzCZAaEekELXWQtts1N3WCkMNxPhgkQ/SqO442FT4JZo3hHJBVTZ9p1ybO2hAHaJ/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="教宗敦促领导人不要利用战争来分散对其他问题的注意力"&gt;战争作为政治策略&lt;/a&gt;来分散选民对国内问题的注意力，这可能被视为对特朗普的进一步批评。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ccMWRjQ7ybCXxcy9MY3O4BpbgiUMTjOiSuqzajoIyBcUjOErP6i27n0mSp7BMbHHZZIuBjqHLdp7pUb2D4tmY3Kaav3ngsciUXFodVeEYr4GsSCz1u5CgJd56SCRcNit9cTfZuXCx1ervtgoFGjW-kIFZr6RyIWWZQr0K84HDqEKagbdnnGs6E2-vhL41ooKnsj8_gqliFZ9pMII5TwChBo6Qm-gdgIp8KjcE1c8GfGL6T3STuwKGLU4tAuLLewoCAVpgSK8lHYwDZWvfNuIdbSHoUdV8aQ6GcDa6w6QmQ0lMQHHjgXufvM7C0Jp0yh-bKLcZL5eZhoVBGQ8IkkYCwsKnrzTRsAiZGm2sX5uWriN0euMzIIy8QKj8Hit5anptFdI3UFHkVt1pQUD5TvQhaH_a1-v-LPFxEj8adbc8hM1UYhSl9YSSavzJC65bs8kNl1RIw1o3a-vgiAPH858trBIgtZgbCI/fW989vwmONSjBC23itEBhj_MtVTAWoCn/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;订阅华盛顿版时事通讯，&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;了解来自美国首都的新闻，并在美国东部时间工作日下午 1 点和 5 点观看彭博电视台的《权力平衡》节目。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;每日图表&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/